                        </bibl>
							              </cit>, but must imply the wish of longevity. Cf. <foreign xml:lang="pra-Latn">vasasatāya</foreign> in EIAD <ref target="#EIAD0021">21</ref>, l. 5 and the commentary thereto.</note>
					          </app>
